&lt;h2 id="add-a-dynamic-navigation">Add a dynamic navigation&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>In Sanity Studio add two new files to &lt;code>/studio/schemas/objects&lt;/code>/. One for &lt;code>link.js&lt;/code> and another for &lt;code>navItem.js&lt;/code>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Inside &lt;code>Link.js&lt;/code> add the following:&lt;/p>
