&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;em>Tip: Hit &lt;code>alt + space&lt;/code> to see the available options at each level of your query&lt;/em>&lt;/p>
